- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the paper deals with a discrete object (folded polygons).
- cs.GR (Graphics) is relevant as the Fréchet distance is often used in computer graphics.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper presents a fixed-parameter tractable algorithm.
